Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's so complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's evil, let's face it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:07.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I know he'll reform
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just give him the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now if you wanna be kind, it'll take some steps so
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Take a seat and I'll explain the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:32.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just be polite, don't bring the worst and- um, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You gotta pay attention first...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's a way to show kindness and trust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Without playing those tricks and rain chaos on us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:39.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No need for those insults, just give it a try
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's gotta be some kind of compassion inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,La la la la la, aa-aa-aa-aa-ahh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though it's hard to make it there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:47.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't hide you care
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Aa-aa-aa-aaahh, la la la la la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Use your magic for the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:55.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And see the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Believe in you in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Thank you Discord for showing me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:05.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That sweetest side that I can now see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Keeping our promise all the more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:13.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause that's what friends are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's so complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's evil, let's face it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I know he'll reform
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:21.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just give him the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So let out that kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't forget where your heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it's not bad! Understand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The friendship we have!